#: forms/templates/forms/rock_cannon_gallery.html:12
msgid ""
"This 100-hole rock cannon tucked away in Parc Meurig is being reclaimed by "
"nature, with its bored holes and carved-out interconnecting grooves almost "
"all covered over by a layer of moss and grass."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r canon carreg 100 twll hwn sydd wedi'i guddio ym Mharc Meurig yn cael "
"ei adfer gan natur, gyda'i dyllau diflas a'i rigolau cydgysylltiedig wedi'u "
"cerfio bron i gyd wedi'u gorchuddio gan haen o fwsogl a glaswellt."

